%python

month = z.z.angular('month')
country = z.z.angular('country')
language = z.z.angular('language')
Top = int(z.z.angular("topN"))

month_dict = {
    '1':'January',
    '2':'February',
    '3':'March',
    '4':'April',
    '5':'May',
    '6':'June',
    '7':'July',
    '8':'August',
    '9':'September',
    '10':'October',
    '11':'November',
    '12':'December'
}

z.z.angularBind( 'nmonth', month_dict[month] )
z.z.angularBind( 'nlanguage', language )
z.z.angularBind( 'ncountry', country )
z.z.angularBind( 'ntop', Top )

strReq3 = """SELECT e_month, e_country_label, m_language, a_full_name, a_type, a_country, a_country_code, a_ethnic, a_group, a_religion, sum(toneneg) as sum_neg_articles, sum(tonepos) as sum_pos_articles, count(*) FROM requete3 where e_month=""" + str(month) + """ AND e_country_label='""" + country + """' AND m_language='""" + language + """' GROUP BY e_month, e_country_label, m_language, a_full_name, a_type"""

"""
# debug
print(country)
print(language)
print(type(Top))
print(strReq3)
"""

if bquorum == True:
   ss3 = SimpleStatement(strReq3, consistency_level=ConsistencyLevel.QUORUM)
   rows = session.execute(ss3)
else :
   rows = session.execute(strReq3)
   
#rows = session.execute(strReq3)
df = rows._current_rows
#print(df.head())
df.columns = ['month', 'country of event', 'language of article', 'actor',  'actor type', 'actor country', 'actor country code', 'actor ethnic', 'actor group', 'actor religion', 'sum negative articles', 'sum positive articles', 'count' ]
#print(df.shape)
df["ratio positive articles"] = df["sum positive articles"] / df["count"] * 100.
df["ratio negative articles"] = df["sum negative articles"] / df["count"] * 100.
